Package: microbs.lu
Title: Process PCR datafiles for the microbs.lu dashboard
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Prasad", "ADHAV", , "prasad.adhav@list.lu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: In Luxembourg the waste water treatment plant samples are used to 
              monitor for epidemic disease such as RSV, Influenye, SARS CoV2 etc.
              This package takes the raw data files from qPCR and ddPCR tests and 
              prepares them for the microbs.lu i.e. Luxembourgish national dashboard.
